{"tid":1390560,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[置頂分析］四條主要戰線 機場 各區狗屋 中聯辦 西九","createTime":"2019-07-31T07:26:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T10:45:26.000Z","uid":191392,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"b0840b1a33efcd27d3bf8874b89fb351d5cdd195","tid":1390560,"uid":191392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T07:26:36.000Z","msg":"前言：<br />\n經過遍地開花，相信大家知邊個區做野最有成效，最安全，最唔會被拉。<br />\n全港基本上每人立場已定，差有無燒到有錢佬同自私港豬。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以係到要發展四條戰線，Keep 住去做，就會贏。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">第一機場</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">經濟壓力</span><br />\n<br />\n唔多講，和你飛行動十分好，對外宣傳亦直指經濟，被壓力有錢佬，建制已經出聲明話我地知做得好。仲要好安全，同埋狗仔唔會出彈。打中外國遊客嘅話...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真心建議一星期接一次朋友，唔洗多，唔洗大量物資同錢，買多D飯盒畀班細路仲好。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">第二狗屋</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">打壓狗隻，加強我方士氣，製造白色恐怖</span><br />\n<br />\n一定係以區做單位，因為上面可以有民眾幫手，要做咩自己諗，大前題Hitandrun <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n記得影低所有可愛嘅狗隻，証件，同埋大頭相， 令<span style=\"color: red;\">老豆可以搵仔</span>。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">第三同四係中聯辦西九</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">革命不是請客吃飯，不是做文章，不是繪畫繡花，不能那樣雅致，那樣從容不迫，文質彬彬，那樣溫良恭儉讓。革命是暴動，是一個階級推翻一個階級的暴烈的行動</span><br />\n<br />\n中聯辦令海外文宣加強，畀壓力中共，西九則係用星火點燃革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n建議大家唔好再分散目標，有要做嘅就做埋，金鐘同其他地方開戰一D都唔值得，記住佢地仲有水炮車，實彈未出，有D地方佢地永遠都唔可以出呢D野 ，你地知邊到架啦 。<br />\n<br />\n同埋我唔想再有手足被捕，大家睇到係港島嘅命運其實真係捱打。<br />\n<br />\n佢地真係無棋架喇，我地就快贏，要贏得轟轟烈烈。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">機場接朋友，西九塞門口</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n------------<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港 時代革命</span>"},{"pid":"fd1e574b1616c16f74e7865adbbb88a92812abe6","tid":1390560,"uid":191392,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T07:27:47.000Z","msg":"我嘅其他諗法，鍾意就睇睇<br />\n<br />\n你知道嗎，只要聯繫匯率玩完，全香港都會一齊收皮。<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dtzckS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dtzckS</a>"},{"pid":"9ed8d22e38b458ea0aee3b09d166c27bed313d96","tid":1390560,"uid":191392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T07:28:10.000Z","msg":"點解我地唔轉守為攻，拎返主導權？<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1379533\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1379533</a>"},{"pid":"9ab2a98022569fa2879a9130e1040f405a32e26d","tid":1390560,"uid":78255,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T07:28:40.000Z","msg":"【8月2號公務員集會】<br />\n到時見！希望冇人會用得著呢張卡片<br />\n<br />\n【8月2日集會】準備咗被補須知嘅卡片打算集會派<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dtBrdS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dtBrdS</a>"},{"pid":"52dd04a92cc219ce238bf4f8d96e8066b351c7a3","tid":1390560,"uid":22011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T07:28:50.000Z","msg":"邊個再講9203係好警察我立即<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dtCufS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dtCufS</a>"},{"pid":"5f3aa9d71d02dda0acdc83cd6da19160f89e921d","tid":1390560,"uid":191392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T07:29:14.000Z","msg":"支持呢四條線幫推下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"319ed910b716231503ea512d7820672c3063d946","tid":1390560,"uid":199257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T07:29:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d51d9ea2f9ee0e5218861f8eb7de91e9a383f4c5","tid":1390560,"uid":191392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20